  "system": {
    "description": "<p>When using <strong>Would You Like Some More?</strong> the target’s desire is no longer limited to the last thing they enjoyed: you can introduce an entirely new desire. This can be something that isn’t present, is unattainable, or doesn’t exist.</p><p>In addition, when activating the <strong>For each additional 3</strong> effect of <strong>Would You Like Some More?</strong>, you can add additional targets equal to ten times the number of 3s rolled. These targets can be anywhere you have access to via direct or indirect means of communication. If they follow somebody who follows you on social media, for example.</p>",
